{"word":"G382 - ἀναρίθμητος - anaríthmētos - an-ar-ith'-may-tos - Innumerable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀναρίθμητος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">anaríthmētos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">an-ar-ith'-may-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Innumerable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"எண்ணிலடங்காத, எண்ணிறந்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"innumerable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G705 - ἀριθμέω - arithméō - ar-ith-meh'-o/705\">G705</a>; <i>unnumbered</i>, that is, <i>without number:</i> - innumerable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}